---
title: Louisiana Cheesy Black Bean Fritter Burger with Potato Wedges & Sweet Chilli Aioli
description: We can bet you've never had fritters quite like this before. With a cheesy black bean patty, soft, brioche-style buns
and a smear of sweet chilli aioli, plus potato wedges, this dish is a real treat.
